com.btc.redg.extractor.model

Class ReferencingEntityModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.btc.redg.extractor.model.EntityModel
      • com.btc.redg.extractor.model.ReferencingEntityModel

  • public class ReferencingEntityModel
extends EntityModel
    This is an EntityModel that basically contains a reference to a complete EntityModel. It should be used to reference entities that might not be in the entity list but are referenced by foreign keys by some known entity.
